Package: dco
Type: Package
Title: Clinical Data Cut-Off Utility
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Seda", "Bayadyan", email = "seda_bayadyan@edu.aua.am", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Seda Bayadyan <seda_bayadyan@edu.aua.am>
Description: A lightweight R package to automate data cut-off (DCO) in clinical trial datasets 
    using configurable YAML rules. Supports filtering, date anonymization, and outcome updates 
    across multiple domains. Designed for flexible use in R projects or local pipelines.
